{"tid":1586522,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【難撚聽過粗口】《飛虎之雷霆極戰》大陸開播：謹以此片獻給英勇的中國香港警察」","createTime":"2019-09-22T04:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T08:02:29.000Z","uid":175314,"like":4,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e3694a3d49ac3122639add91e90c9e445b03833e","tid":1586522,"uid":175314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h15rj2R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh15rj2R.jpg&h=cb10331d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WEtDVBc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWEtDVBc.jpg&h=ec0d5d0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/article/yB3lnE?utm_source=copyshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Farticle%2FyB3lnE%3Futm_source%3Dcopyshare&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FSwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=45924392\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/HK/article/yB3lnE?utm_source=copyshare</a><br />\n<br />\n緊接《街坊財爺》播出的，曾經有消息指是《飛虎之雷霆極戰》，不過最後確定是黃心穎和張振朗主演的《牛下女高音》，在警察和黃心穎之間作出取捨實在不容易，不過無綫最後選了後者。香港未播，不過<span style=\"color: red;\">《飛虎之雷霆極戰》已經在大陸率先開播，片頭還有字幕：「謹以此片獻給英勇的中國香港警察。」</span>如果在香港播放時都有此字幕，未知觀眾會有甚麼反應？<br />\n<br />\n由苗僑偉、黃宗澤、吳卓羲、馬國明和吳啟華主演的劇集《飛虎之雷霆極戰》，還有示威者們最愛的「唯唯」梁競徽。故事都係講飛虎係the best of the best of the best嗰啲，不過官方微博出了一些劇中對白截圖，都相當敏感，例如馬國明話：「沒錯，我曾經開槍誤殺同僚。」黃宗澤又話：「我知道大家可能因為這件事會覺得很失望、無助或迷茫。」還有三哥苗僑偉：「其實每個警察心目中都有一份使命感，這份使命感不止說要打擊罪案，而是要盡我們能力保護好身邊每一個人。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n完美演繹咩係難撚聽過粗口"},{"pid":"86e53d3b934eb40c90f58f90e4d6600c9d1a20c2","tid":1586522,"uid":258409,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:08:39.000Z","msg":"祝全部早日殉職？"},{"pid":"4aecfd6361c9cd8cf5a7af07609645fcafbf1607","tid":1586522,"uid":255105,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:15:12.000Z","msg":"不如唔好拍飛虎，改拍速龍？反正都同一班狗"},{"pid":"65199c999315a41b140b867321f007a2abbb2064","tid":1586522,"uid":175314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4aecfd6361c9cd8cf5a7af07609645fcafbf1607","tid":1586522,"uid":255105,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:15:12.000Z","msg":"不如唔好拍飛虎，改拍速龍？反正都同一班狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:22:13.000Z","msg":"咸狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea16155547bba261ce0839c6b5fd8f199a23f94","tid":1586522,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:38:48.000Z","msg":"拍套休班警"},{"pid":"67a9bead5057b0e7eed707dc97c5e676cd14fbeb","tid":1586522,"uid":247122,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:42:09.000Z","msg":"&quot;在警察和黃心穎之間作出取捨實在不容易&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8288b92213939668f1f37a7257c3e5824e1a1e","tid":1586522,"uid":55936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:21:53.000Z","msg":"完美KO賓穎"},{"pid":"adf8f3d32adee7686d0d0da7f06de7bb59d3ac1a","tid":1586522,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:23:43.000Z","msg":"Tvb 你唔係唔跟下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e706b10f4b6a2c17d1e047bef49c98f2793ff4a8","tid":1586522,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86e53d3b934eb40c90f58f90e4d6600c9d1a20c2","tid":1586522,"uid":258409,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:08:39.000Z","msg":"祝全部早日殉職？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:25:19.000Z","msg":"拎去狗火化場"},{"pid":"312efbc997a7de5b8db5f499a4ff1fab8bcdbf5e","tid":1586522,"uid":126210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"repl